snippet.title: Light Gun Reviews 58: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Mutant & Monster Mayhem (Plug and Play)
snippet.description: Review of Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Mutant & Monster Mayhem made by WayForward Technologies in 2005. It is a plug and play device released by Tech 2 Go LLC. WayForward is famous for the games of the Shantae series.
